ChangeLog for the SM2 Message API Specification
===============================================

Version 0.4
===========
- Changed the way error handling is taking place.  It is now done through
  the Error object as opposed to the error() function returning a string.
  Read doc/error_handling.txt in SquirrelMail 2 for more information.
- Removed the error() function
- Redefined the $error variable

Previous Versions
=================
- Set up all necessary functions for basic functionality.
